title: Who is Sam Pepper? Firework incident in India leads to streamer’s permanent Kick ban and huge backlash
description: London streamer Sam Pepper faced a permanent ban after a firework injured a young girl during his Diwali livestream in New Delhi. The incident occurred on October 20. A rocket went astray, striking the girl near her eye. Pepper apologized and covered medical costs. The platform cited safety concerns for the ban. This event sparks discussions on livestream safety regulations.
